txt.en: George seems incredibly agitated about something. Perhaps you should try and find out what it is.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>WARNING: This quest begins a special session quest. You will be logged out of your normal character and take on the guise of a player-friendly npc. You will attain a set of skills unique to this special player character.</rgb>
Having had a taste of freedom, you desire more.
You think that perhaps it is time to escape Farmer Sandson's coop.
